Package com.example.freeturilo.core

Class Location

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.freeturilo.core.Location
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Favourite, IdentifiedLocation, Station
    public class Location
extends java.lang.Object
    A named geographical location.

    Object of this class represents a distinguished real-world location and encapsulates information about its name, latitude and longitude. There are multiple methods declared within the class that help represent a location with text or a map marker.

    Version:
    1.0.0
    Author:
    Mikołaj Terzyk
    See Also:
    name, latitude, longitude, getPrimaryText(), getSecondaryText(android.content.Context), getInlineSecondaryText(android.content.Context), getTertiaryText(android.content.Context), createMarkerOptions(android.content.Context)
